    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This unit features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a complete VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to maintain torsional rigidity. The naturally aspirated power delivery remains sharp across the rev range, complemented by a communicative chassis and responsive steering rack. While the exterior and interior exhibit minor wear consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed in for peak performance.",
