    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, with just the usual minor wear you\u2019d expect from a car that's been enjoyed. It\u2019s super clean, super comfy, and honestly just a joy to drive. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come by and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road!",
